2.title: The Wedding of the Season
2.plot: Laura and Ernesto have sent out 400 invitations to their wedding at the Capitale, and they're getting back more yes responses than they expected thus presenting a major challenge for Josh and Jung. Also, Fete is throwing a kid-friendly going away party.

3.title: Episode #1.3
3.plot: Jeffrey and Marisa are getting married in an intimate, Gilded-Age ceremony at Alder House, a ramshackle mansion, and he needs everything to be exactly right. In the middle of the madness, Jung's creating an eco-friendly 30th birthday blowout for Courtney.

4.title: Episode #1.4
4.plot: Fete staffer Erin is about to get married, and when the planner she hired is nowhere to be found, Josh and Jung step in. Good friend Marianne wants Josh and Jung to transform a gritty music hall into an elegant 40's supper club for her CD release party.

5.title: Episode #1.5
5.plot: Josh and Jung love clients Mike and Qian, but getting the busy lawyers to take time to focus on their wedding is next to impossible. Andy has hired Fete to throw a party to celebrate the anniversary of his bike tour company and he has high expectations.

6.title: Episode #1.6
6.plot: Popular couple Laura and Ernesto have sent out 400 invitations to their wedding at New York's Capitale, and they're getting back more yes responses than they expected. Big weddings are no problem for the Fete team, but the biggest wedding Josh and Jung have ever done at Capitale was for 220 people. Will Jung be able to design an event that will feel elegant but fit all of Laura and Ernesto's guests? Meanwhile, Josh and Jung's friend Will is moving with his wife and five year-old daughter to Bali, and Fete is throwing a kid-friendly going away party for them.

2.title: Under the Wire Wedding
2.plot: Alexa and Jorge are getting married in just three weeks and want Fete to design a classic outdoor affair at Alexa's family's landmark estate in the countryside. Jung and Josh also put together a 70's-themed birthday party at New York's hip New Museum.

locations: New York City, New York, USA
imdb.plot outline: Wedded to Perfection follows the charismatic owners of Fete Events, spouses Jung Lee and Josh Brooks, as they plan and execute some of the most high-end weddings in New York. Jung is the real force behind the duo and is on the front lines dealing with their demanding clients. With behind-the-scenes action leading up to the "big day," Wedded to Perfection gives ultimate access to some of most elegant and masterfully-crafted receptions.
